                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: #7A5195;">1987: Ide Awal</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Thomas & John Knoll mengembangkan program 'Display' untuk gambar skala abu-abu.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
